result.name: 湘薈

reviews.text: Cuisines are mostly hot and spicy, but you are offered the choice to have a less spicy version (for hot dishes only). Services are great, there will be a nice lady to greet you and help you out when you have trouble in ordering. This is a good place for family gathering, cozy and quite place to talk.
酸菜魚無魚味，炒猪腰非常差，價錢不配合菜式質素，垃圾！中伏

偶然發現新開的湖南菜，點了酸菜魚和農家小炒（總覺得農家小炒能試出一間湖南菜的真功夫），味道不錯。最貼心的是餐廳是用金鳳米，煮出黎的飯非常好吃，要讚一下(經理話用的是金鳳米）。價錢中等，環境乾淨。一定會再去！
Found this newly opened Hunan restaurant and decided to give a try. Ordered soup fish with pickles and sliced pork fried with green chili, both taste nice. What surprised me is the rice, very well cooked come as complimentary. Will definitely visit again!
試左午餐，貴，味道一般
味道一般，份量太少。
